2007-11-22  Israel Herraiz <herraiz@gsyc.escet.urjc.es>

	* mccabe/mccabe:

	Adding SLOC count per function to the McCabe utility.
	Now, this utility calculates the SLOC, cyclomatic completixity
	and number of returns for each function. If there is no
	function, it calculates the values for the whole file.
	
